OL,6,FA 92-year-old amputee who threatened
OL,7,Fto stab care home staff had "ample
OL,8,Fopportunity" to drop his knife before
OL,9,Fofficers pepper sprayed and tasered
OL,10,Fhim, a court has heard.
OL,12,FPc Stephen Smith, 51, faces trial
OL,13,Falongside his colleague Pc Rachel
OL,14,FComotto, 36, for allegedly using
OL,15,Fexcessive force on Donald Burgess
OL,16,Fduring an incident at Park Beck care
OL,17,Fhome in St Leonards-on-Sea, East
OL,18,FSussex, in June 2022.
