OL,3,COfficer who used spray on amputee, 92,
OL,4,Cdid not see he was disabled, court told
OL,6,FMr Burgess was taken to hospital after
OL,7,Fthe incident and later contracted
OL,8,FCovid. He died 22 days later aged 93.
OL,10,FThe care home had called 999 after Mr
OL,11,FBurgess, a single-leg amputee and
OL,12,Fwheelchair user, reportedly grabbed a
OL,13,Fknife and threatened to stab staff.
OL,15,FSmith, who gave evidence on Thursday,
OL,16,Ftold the jury sitting at Southwark
OL,17,FCrown Court he did not see that Mr
OL,18,FBurgess was disabled and using a
OL,19,Fwheelchair as he was focused on the
OL,20,Fknife the pensioner was holding in his
OL,21,Fhand.
