OL,6,FIn the Sussex Police "use of force
OL,7,Fform" which Smith filled out shortly
OL,8,Fafter the incident, he wrote Mr
OL,9,FBurgess had been "given ample
OL,10,Fopportunity" to drop the knife before
OL,11,FComotto and himself resorted to force.
OL,13,FSmith also told the court one of the
OL,14,Ffirst things he noticed when entering
OL,15,FMr Burgess's room was that he had
OL,16,F"white knuckles".
OL,18,FSmith said: "That indicated to me that
OL,19,Fhe had an immense grip on that knife."
