OL,6,FWhen asked by his defence barrister
OL,7,FDenis Barry what his goal was at the
OL,8,Ftime, Smith said: "To make sure no-one
OL,9,Fgot injured and look after everyone
OL,10,Fwithin the care home."
OL,12,FEarlier this week, jurors heard that
OL,13,FSmith allegedly emptied a full
OL,14,Fcanister of synthetic Pava spray into
OL,15,FMr Burgess's face and struck him with
OL,16,Fa baton, with Comotto deploying her
OL,17,FTaser ` all within one minute and 23
OL,18,Fseconds of entering his room.
